entry.title: Batlez/Batlez-Tweaks
entry.summary: Batlez Tweaks is a batch tweaking script that optimizes your system to provide the best gaming experience possible by lowering latency, increasing FPS, and decreasing background processes. It is free and open-source. Works on any PC!
